$ System.Runtime.InteropServices.Marshal: SystemDefaultCharSize / SystemMaxDBCSCharSize

`SystemDefaultCharSize` corresponds to the size (in bytes) of a → Microsoft/dot-net/namespaces-classes/System/Char[`System.Char`] on the system (2 for
→ development/Unicode, 1 for → development/Unicode/ASCII systems).:w

`SystemMaxDBCSCharSize ` corresponds to the maximum size of the double byte character set (DBCS) for the current OS. 
